Don't overlook the remainder of the quote, when taken as a whole it gives a much greater significance to it."The tree of liberty must be refreshed from time to time with the blood of patriots and tyrants. It is it’s natural manure."ATTRIBUTION:	THOMAS JEFFERSON, letter to William Stephens Smith, November 13, 1787True Patriots understand this.